    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">California doctor convicted of $45M Medicare fraud scheme that funded luxury vacations and a $12K crossbow</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      California doctor accused of submitting $45 million in false Medicare claims for Botox injections was convicted of wire fraud and obstruction charges.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/05/19/california-doctor-convicted-45m-medicare-fraud-scheme-funded-luxury-vacations-12k-crossbow/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
