        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Man allegedly called 911 multiple times to report zombies, ghosts and a UFO, then claimed to be a cop</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      West Virginia man arrested after repeatedly calling 911 to report zombies, ghosts, and a UFO at his home, according to the Randolph County Sheriff.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/05/19/man-allegedly-called-911-multiple-times-report-zombies-ghosts-ufo-claimed-cop/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
