        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Community grieves the 3 men killed while defending San Diego mosque</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Authorities say the three people killed by two teen shooters at a San Diego mosque died while saving roughly 140 children who were in the building at the time of the attack.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/05/19/community-grieves-beloved-san-diego-mosque-security-guard-killed-on-the-job/"  >(Jaimie Ding, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
