        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump endorses Ken Paxton in Texas GOP primary, boosting his challenge to incumbent Sen. Cornyn</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Donald Trump has endorsed Texas Attorney General Ken Paxton, supercharging his effort to oust incumbent Sen. John Cornyn in a Republican primary runoff.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/05/19/trump-endorses-paxton-in-texas-republican-primary-boosting-his-challenge-to-incumbent-sen-cornyn/"  >(Thomas Beaumont, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
