        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Virginia teacher shot by 6-year-old says boy showed &#8216;violent&#8217; warning signs &#8211; assistant principal now on trial</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Teacher Abby Zwerner testified the 6-year-old who shot her had been acting defiant, describing warning signs she reported before the classroom attack.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/05/19/virginia-teacher-shot-6-year-old-says-boy-showed-violent-warning-signs-assistant-principal-trial/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
