      <img src="/static14/us/2026/05/19/kentucky-primary-the-latest-test-of-trumps-power-in-gop-as-he-looks-to-oust-us-rep-thomas-massie.webp" alt="US Rep. Thomas Massie loses Kentucky GOP primary to Ed Gallrein in another victory for Trump" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">US Rep. Thomas Massie loses Kentucky GOP primary to Ed Gallrein in another victory for Trump</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Kentucky U.S. Rep. Thomas Massie has lost his Republican House primary after a concerted effort by President Donald Trump to oust him through challenger and ultimate winner Ed Gallrein.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/05/19/kentucky-primary-the-latest-test-of-trumps-power-in-gop-as-he-looks-to-oust-us-rep-thomas-massie/"  >(Jesse Bedayn And Dylan Lovan, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 19 May 2026 17:25:59 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 19 May 2026 17:25:59 GMT">
