      <img src="/static14/us/2026/05/19/south-carolina-republicans-press-toward-house-vote-on-congressional-redistricting-plan.webp" alt="South Carolina House backs congressional map favoring GOP but bill faces a more skeptical Senate" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">South Carolina House backs congressional map favoring GOP but bill faces a more skeptical Senate</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The South Carolina House has endorsed a plan to redraw its congressional districts to favor Republicans at the urging of President Donald Trump.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/05/19/south-carolina-republicans-press-toward-house-vote-on-congressional-redistricting-plan/"  >(Jeffrey Collins And David A. Lieb, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
