    <p itemprop="text">
      The World Health Organization director-general has expressed concern over the rapid spread of a rare type of Ebola in eastern Congo.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/19/congo-reports-more-ebola-cases-as-who-expresses-concern-over-scale-and-speed-of-the-outbreak/"  >(Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
