    <h3 itemprop="headline">Xi and Putin meet to reaffirm China-Russia ties days after Trump&#8217;s visit to Beijing</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Chinese leader Xi Jinping has welcomed Russian President Vladimir Putin in Beijing in a meeting meant to reaffirm ties days after a visit by U.S. President Donald Trump to China.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/20/xi-and-putin-meet-to-reaffirm-china-russia-ties-days-after-trumps-visit-to-beijing/"  >(E. Eduardo Castillo And Simina Mistreanu, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
