    <h3 itemprop="headline">Board of Peace will ask the UN Security Council to press Hamas to disarm</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The body overseeing the U.S.-brokered ceasefire in Gaza plans to ask the United Nations Security Council to press Hamas to disarm.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/05/19/board-of-peace-will-ask-the-un-security-council-to-press-hamas-to-disarm/"  >(Jamey Keaten And Elena Becatoros, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
