        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">AWS adds Advanced Prompt Optimization tool to Bedrock</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      AWS late on Thursday added a new prompt optimization tool to Amazon Bedrock, its fully managed service for building, deploying, and scaling generative AI applications.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/15/aws-adds-advanced-prompt-optimization-tool-to-bedrock/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 20 May 2026 04:15:00 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 20 May 2026 04:15:00 GMT">
