        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Microsoft business software faces UK antitrust probe over bundling, AI lock-in</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The UK’s competition regulator has launched a broad antitrust investigation into Microsoft’s business software ecosystem, opening a new front in growing regulatory scrutiny of how cloud platforms, productivity software, and embedded AI capabilities may affect competition in enterprise technology mar
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/15/microsoft-business-software-faces-uk-antitrust-probe-over-bundling-ai-lock-in/"  >(Computer World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
