        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Apple&#8217;s App Store model for AI</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Apple has a design for AI life. It hopes to build on the outstanding hardware performance its systems already provide to create a fantastic environment in which AI developers can thrive.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/14/apples-app-store-model-for-ai/"  >(Computer World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
