    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The OpenAI lawsuit became a master class in what not to put in writing</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Elon Musk’s loss in his lawsuit against Sam Altman and OpenAI, decided on Monday by a jury and upheld by a judge, wasn’t the only damaging revelation to emerge from the California courtroom.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/05/19/the-openai-lawsuit-became-a-masterclass-in-what-not-to-put-in-writing/"  >(Chris Stokel-Walker, Fast Company)</a>
