    <h3 itemprop="headline">Andy Barr bests crowded Senate primary with help from Trump on way to replacing McConnell</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Rep. Andy Barr topped an 11-person Kentucky Republican Senate primary, powered by Trump&apos;s endorsement, to vie for retiring Sen. McConnell&apos;s seat.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/05/19/barr-bests-crowded-senate-primary-help-from-trump-way-replacing-mcconnell/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
