    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump-backed governor wins GOP primary for third term after running on deregulation and tax cuts</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Gov. Brad Little, backed by President Trump, won Idaho&apos;s Republican gubernatorial primary against seven challengers to pursue a third term in office.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/05/20/trump-backed-governor-wins-gop-primary-third-term-deregulation-tax-cuts/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
